OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FPaddington The Musical was the big
OL,7,Fwinner at the 2026 Olivier Awards,
OL,8,Fwhere the West End revivals of Evita
OL,9,Fand Into The Woods also won plaudits.
OL,11,FThe smash-hit musical ` which is
OL,12,Fadapted from the books by Michael Bond
OL,13,Fand the hit films ` won in seven
OL,14,Fcategories from 11 nominations,
OL,15,Fincluding best new musical, best actor
OL,16,Fin a musical and best actor and
OL,17,Factress in a supporting role.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
