OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FIt follows the adventures of the
OL,7,Fmarmalade-loving bear from Peru,
OL,8,Fstarring a life-like puppet of
OL,9,FPaddington, and also picked up the
OL,10,Fprize for best costume design, best
OL,11,Fset design and the Sir Peter Hall
OL,12,Faward for best director.
OL,14,FPaddington The Musical, which is
OL,15,Fcurrently being staged at the Savoy
OL,16,FTheatre in London, features music
OL,17,Fwritten by McFly star Tom Fletcher,
OL,18,Fand its book was written by playwright
OL,19,FJessica Swale.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
