OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the awards ceremony
OL,7,Fat Royal Albert Hall, Swale hailed
OL,8,Fworking with Fletcher as "really fun"
OL,9,Fand said: "It's such a privilege to
OL,10,Flook after such a special bear. It's
OL,11,Fjust been so fun. We've had the
OL,12,Fgreatest adventure."
OL,14,FITV News caught up with several stars
OL,15,Fbefore they went into the Royal Albert
OL,16,FHall
