OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FAmerican actress Rachel Zegler picked
OL,7,Fup the award for best actress in a
OL,8,Fmusical for her West End debut in the
OL,9,Frevival of Evita at the London
OL,10,FPalladium, which drew large outdoor
OL,11,Fcrowds while she sang Don't Cry For Me
OL,12,FArgentina from an outside balcony.
OL,14,FThe critically acclaimed show, which
OL,15,Ffollows the life of Argentine
OL,16,Fpolitician Eva Peron and her rise from
OL,17,Factress to first lady, also saw Fabian
OL,18,FAloise take home the Gillian Lynne
OL,19,FAward for best theatre choreographer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
