OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FInto The Woods, which was tied with
OL,7,FPaddington The Musical with 11
OL,8,Fnominations, also picked up two
OL,9,FOlivier Awards for best musical
OL,10,Frevival and best lighting.
OL,12,FElsewhere, Rosamund Pike ` known for
OL,13,Fon-screen roles including Gone Girl `
OL,14,Fpicked up the prize for best actress
OL,15,Ffor her return to the stage after
OL,16,Falmost 14 years.
OL,18,FJack Holden won the award for best
OL,19,Factor for Kenrex at The Other Palace,
OL,20,Fand the play also picked up the prize
OL,21,Ffor best sound design.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
