OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FPaapa Essiedu took home the gong for
OL,7,Fbest actor in a supporting role for
OL,8,FAll My Sons at Wyndham's Theatre, and
OL,9,Fthe play was also crowned best revival.
OL,11,FPunch, based on the true story of a
OL,12,Fteenager who killed a man with a
OL,13,Fsingle punch, also won two awards and
OL,14,Ftook home the prizes for best actress
OL,15,Fin a supporting role and best new play.
