OL,3,CPaddington The Musical sweeps Oliviers
OL,4,Cas Evita also triumphs
OL,6,FThis year's Olivier Awards marked the
OL,7,F50th anniversary of the ceremony and
OL,8,Fwere hosted by comedian Nick Mohammed.
OL,10,FIt featured a string of musical
OL,11,Ftheatre performances, with a cameo
OL,12,Ffrom Paddington the bear himself
OL,13,Fsinging a rendition of Marmalade from
OL,14,Fthe smash-hit musical.
OL,16,FElsewhere in the ceremony, Zegler
OL,17,Fbelted out Don't Cry For Me Argentina
OL,18,Fand there were performances from Into
OL,19,FThe Woods and Phantom Of The Opera.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
